{"type": "article", "id": 17834, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-11-20T07:02:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 19037, "name": ":OTVETDESIGN"}, {"id": 19038, "name": "Drill design"}, {"id": 19039, "name": "Quantum Bakery LLC"}, {"id": 19040, "name": "Atelier Robotiq"}, {"id": 19041, "name": "Stable Goods"}, {"id": 19042, "name": "Anna Mo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 83, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060600425038LujtVlCbfgsFQ5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tFiber Pattern Lamp by Atelier Robotiq\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这些灯的灯罩使用了特殊的航空纤维材料，通过控制机器人完成，有点像一个 UFO。它的重量甚至轻于一个 iPhone6，当光线透过网格灯罩投影在墙上，有清晰的网格阴影，比手工编织的网格灯罩多了一份未来感。直径 25 英寸，售价 370 欧元，有多种颜色可选，<a href=\"http://www.atelierrobotiq.com/shop/fiber-pattern-lamp\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101523blVW68SHuEBirchT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.721\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101523SRjfx5td6nDpNorh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101524o4unYgf6eUS8bJBV.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.31333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101524G9HJQ38ZXkbqydW5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101525Qc2Ll40mENA9ntja.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tPint by Stable Goods\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个可以上下拧开的水壶，底座上的大圆盖拧下来可以转到壶嘴的盖子上，变成一个高脚杯。此外，能打开的底座也很方便清洗。水壶表面像灰色的大理石，带给水壶一种典雅的气质，它其实用了两层不锈钢，有很好的保温效果。产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/367705503/the-pint-a-canteen-that-converts-to-a-cup\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101525KfDeulnhMNTt536p.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75096525\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071015317BZjhdNWCfkpmX5u.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101531eyOCrnuLwKfDNpFj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071015326tCWvqSlNuGoDZiK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101532Raqwh4FMp9KuoxfJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\toffset by Drill design\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这款名为“offset”的木椅来自日本的设计工作室 Drill design，原本应该连接在一起的靠背和座位相互交叉，上下构成两个圆环。藤编座椅和靠背用了不同的颜色区分，使高脚凳似的座椅更明显，是很特别的结构。椅子可以两个重叠起来，它有两种靠背，一种是西式的环形靠背，一种是仿明式。<a href=\"http://www.drill-design.com/work-furniture/offset\" target=\"_blank\">这里是设计师的主页。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101533XBmTZ2r8HdnvV7Iy.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101533P3sDp9JX84LKuoba.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101533cDG5P1C8wHarqJF3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.1002445\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101534Ex8s3mwFUyLbNofq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.11613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101534xnohODJtYPH0Lam1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.1002445\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tFigment by Quantum Bakery LLC\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个手机壳，但在壳子上折叠安装了一个虚拟实境装置，翻转到手机屏幕前就可以看 VR 视频了。此外，镜片本身也是一个手机支架，简易而方便。来自美国硅谷的团队 Quantum Bakery 开发了这款产品，有黑白两色可选，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/quantumbakery/figment-vr-virtual-reality-in-your-pocket\" target=\"_blank\">目前正在众筹，</a>预计明年上市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101535xaeBl3R4P7yEAYX8.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101538C5B8x6FQglWqXVjL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50294118\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101539gNClOqXkHwfri0V3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101539yqpUdeoI6cYC37WO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101540cXCjkneDrT0tLPV5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63529412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710154065lGskBJd7p9vzLf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tSUPER LUSH pet bed by Anna Mo\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是乌克兰的设计师 Anna Mo 自制的宠物小窝，她购买了产自澳洲的美丽诺羊毛和两根超大的木针，手工编成粗线条的交叉纹路，在柔软舒适之余带去温暖的感受。此外，她还编织了衣服，使粗线条的羊毛像一片片树叶，有 15 种颜色可选，目前在 etsy 上出售，<a href=\"http://www.etsy.com/listing/245166707/super-lush-pet-bed-cozy-basket-for-dog?ref=shop_home_active_24\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101540McTuSsahoBObNlvP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101541h3PIMQiloYwvUT7B.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.795\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101541EDAkCYLlQ7NxnBm2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.795\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710154226qwnK5fLDdae9oI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.795\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101542LxNEzsVb5ctY62IP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.795\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tYarmarka by :OTVETDESIGN \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t购买大米小麦之类的谷物通常是不需要包装的，一个透明的袋子足可说明一切。俄罗斯的 Yarmarka 坚持使用纸盒包装，他们请来设计事务所 :OTVETDESIGN 做包装设计。在彩色的盒子正中间画了一个口袋，中间印着对应的粮食，一头连接着叉子，表达可食用的概念。四周环绕着更大的颗粒和使用说明，用了有手绘感的图案，很直观。重要的是盒子带给人清新活泼的感受，近似于饼干等零食，让人觉得亲近生动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101542AR8znvBxbcip3UQ1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101543W0BYOmaJlfU6SDx3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101544aSMdD4e0xbo7CfPB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101544n8qYkHWAKDMZpdOU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101545B5EUmGkr3Hi4zAKL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101545XRxwOAyhElbMH3WS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}